    <string name="help_credits">
        The goal of VAPORSKULL is to uncover all the skulls on the game board by using the least number of scans possible.
        Selecting a pink box will either reveal a skull or use a scan to count and display the total number of hidden
        skulls in the row and column corresponding to that box. You can also select a revealed skull to trigger a scan in a similar manner.
        When all skulls are revealed, the game is over and you win.
